am\": \"the sole distance event\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1158}, {\"ngram\": \"barriers\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"reportsthe Mirror\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Participants must clear a series of both wet and dry jumps across a 3,000m distance, equivalent to seven-and-a-half laps of the track.\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Participants\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"a 3,000m distance\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"seven-and-a-half laps\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In total, there are 28 fixed barriers and seven water jumps to be negotiated, with the latter of these usually placed on a separate part of the track to the main running surface.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"total\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"28 fixed barriers\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"seven water\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"a separate part\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"the main running surface\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike other events, the barriers in the steeplechase are fixed, allowing athletes to step on them and push off, rather than having to hurdle them entirely.\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other events\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"the barriers\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"the steeplechase\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1569}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the men's event, these barriers stand at 91.4cm high, while